# riddance

A tool designed to remove bloatware and restore freedom

## Prerequisites

- [Python](https://www.python.org/downloads/)

- [pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installation/)

## Installation

```shell
python -m pip install --user riddance
```

